    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of July 3 obituary about Rolf Mageren; he died May 5, not June 3</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An obituary yesterday about Rolf Mageren, a German businessman who escaped a World War II British internment camp in India disguised as an Englishman, misstated the date of his death. It was May 5, not June 3.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>An obituary yesterday about Rolf Mageren, a German businessman who escaped a World War II British internment camp in India disguised as an Englishman, misstated the date of his death. It was May 5, not June 3.</p>
        <p>Correction:  July 5, 2000, Wednesday  A correction in this space yesterday of the date of death in an obituary on Monday of a German businessman who escaped from a British internment camp in World War II misspelled the man's surname. He was Rolf Magener, not Mageren.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="correction_text">
        <p>Correction: July 5, 2000, Wednesday</p>
        <p>A correction in this space yesterday of the date of death in an obituary on Monday of a German businessman who escaped from a British internment camp in World War II misspelled the man's surname. He was Rolf Magener, not Mageren.</p>
        <p>&lt;br&gt;</p>
        <p>&lt;br&gt;</p>
      </block>
